<p>
    <textarea id="textArea_StagesGraph" style="width:400px;height:200px;">@Model.ObserveEnvironment.RenderGraphOfRelationships(@Model.CurrentMonitor, @Model.CurrentMonitor.StageObjectRelationships)</textarea>
